data.description: ~ No Structural/Expensive Issues ~ Newer Furnace/Water Heater & AC ~ Fantastic home on a half acre lot nestled in the Ponderosa Pines on a quiet cul-de-sac! This property is perfectly located in a private area full of trees, but is still close to everything: walking distance to Fox Run Regional Park, minutes to I25, award winning D20 schools and restraints/shopping nearby.   This home has two walkouts, from the family room and basement to a fully fenced back yard.  Only some minor updating for Instant Equity in this home!
